0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你可以買無風扇散熱器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://www.dvhardware.net/news/2012/silverstone_heligon_he02_3.jpg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dvhardware.net%2Fnews%2F2012%2Fsilverstone_heligon_he02_3.jpg%22&d=CmemZmFyzWbYnZ7Ld0a%2FVk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4a50d1e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dvhardware.net/news/2012/silverstone_heligon_he02_3.jpg&quot;</a>  /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n呢種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  超大舊但真係唔會嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細嚿啲嘅塔式 加把慢速 風扇 已經唔會點嘈啦 唔使咁誇張呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實兩舊水到既塔式散熱已經靜過原裝好多，散熱都好過原裝"},{"pid":"b33c433850d9df778c9a9352a36c2c61b4ed20fd","tid":422182,"uid":78961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你可以買無風扇散熱器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://www.dvhardware.net/news/2012/silverstone_heligon_he02_3.jpg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dvhardware.net%2Fnews%2F2012%2Fsilverstone_heligon_he02_3.jpg%22&d=CmemZmFyzWbYnZ7Ld0a%2FVk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4a50d1e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dvhardware.net/news/2012/silverstone_heligon_he02_3.jpg&quot;</a>  /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n呢種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  超大舊但真係唔會嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細嚿啲嘅塔式 加把慢速 風扇 已經唔會點嘈啦 唔使咁誇張呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實兩舊水到既塔式散熱已經靜過原裝好多，散熱都好過原裝</blockquote><br />\n其實個塔散得切, 風扇唔洗開咁大, 就會靜<br />\n有多餘錢就預多少少, 買隻gelid tranquillo 二百幾蚊"},{"pid":"fc09d7aa862d7cf99a33726a90175a9f7988a8c0","tid":422182,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T18:53:59.000Z","msg":"2手cooler master 212x 應該150有找"},{"pid":"9757cb3f9fb1dc799115d00223e374541d0ae1a5","tid":422182,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:11:12.000Z","msg":"amd原廠散熱風扇好雞"},{"pid":"6259b06ef852225e698e5bcece0be762228bf9f1","tid":422182,"uid":48022,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:21:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔該曬各位真係答嘢嘅巴打<br />\nBtw第一次喺硬件台問嘢，估唔到咁多on9仔</blockquote><br />\n其實佢地見到你budget太低,推薦唔到佢地認為合格嘅產品所以就鬧你<br />\n150冇錯真係買唔起大多數cooler,包括無風扇大大舊果D<br />\n我會再俾多個建議你<br />\n<br />\n風扇嘈主要原因係CPU溫度上升<br />\n你可以用80蚊買Gelid GC-Extreme<br />\n全機清塵順手拆左你個CPU Cooler再換散熱膏<br />\n咁樣唔駛換新CPU Cooler都可以靜返<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">其實唔係個個都係巴打,我係絲打</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"0252055c9452e9585ea5276b10e2d22ae9afb63b","tid":422182,"uid":18790,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔該曬各位真係答嘢嘅巴打<br />\nBtw第一次喺硬件台問嘢，估唔到咁多on9仔</blockquote><br />\n其實佢地見到你budget太低,推薦唔到佢地認為合格嘅產品所以就鬧你<br />\n150冇錯真係買唔起大多數cooler,包括無風扇大大舊果D<br />\n我會再俾多個建議你<br />\n<br />\n風扇嘈主要原因係CPU溫度上升<br />\n你可以用80蚊買Gelid GC-Extreme<br />\n全機清塵順手拆左你個CPU Cooler再換散熱膏<br />\n咁樣唔駛換新CPU Cooler都可以靜返<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">其實唔係個個都係巴打,我係絲打</span></span></div></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母死人妖<br />\n咪比人篤爆咗你係千早狗囉"},{"pid":"e73c6e98c64cc40b881173