blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諗緊 cooler Master hyper tx3 定vortex plus, 好似差唔多？</blockquote><br />\n建議你跟我上面講嘅方法做左先,試下work唔work<br />\n真係唔work再儲多幾百蚊換隻cooler<br />\n你果粒係咩CPU?</blockquote><br />\nAmd phenom ii x 4 840<br />\n<br />\n我check佢idle得3x度<br />\n但一開機已經勁嘈，用咩software可以睇到佢rpm?</blockquote><br />\n過來人 換212就靜晒 如果你打算入bios調慢轉速唔理溫度只會加快電腦死亡"},{"pid":"c380baeba182926f0f89f02e095f433b81386c0a","tid":422182,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:52:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諗緊 cooler Master hyper tx3 定vortex plus, 好似差唔多？</blockquote><br />\n建議你跟我上面講嘅方法做左先,試下work唔work<br />\n真係唔work再儲多幾百蚊換隻cooler<br />\n你果粒係咩CPU?</blockquote><br />\nAmd phenom ii x 4 840<br />\n<br />\n我check佢idle得3x度<br />\n但一開機已經勁嘈，用咩software可以睇到佢rpm?</blockquote><br />\nHWMonitor<br />\n不過你CPU好舊,我建議你清完塵就算,風扇嘈都冇辦法<br />\n如果可以就唔理佢直到升級/換電腦<br />\n150蚊幫唔到你D咩,加少少用Gelid Tranquillo Rev.4可能有幫助"},{"pid":"945dcb806b5d76e9464c0977689b7343cdaea0e4","tid":422182,"uid":22817,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:29:01.000Z","msg":"你聽軟飯王9up死得仲快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea5429148c2507b0855f509039145b847014c8e","tid":422182,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T20:48:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你聽軟飯王9up死得仲快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽你講打機裝ssd死鳩埋啦r水吹哥 洗唔洗借d fd比你？"},{"pid":"7ea0b51862f0a21900f36e64c345ae5b0e1efc64","tid":422182,"uid":22817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你聽軟飯王9up死得仲快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽你講打機裝ssd死鳩埋啦r水吹哥 洗唔洗借d fd比你？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/081912_3dcd03a5b2d99eb0ef52dc66f58a54a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eserv